short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Facilitate navigation with keyboard for accessibility user and power user

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
PowerNav allows users to quickly navigate to and interact with navigation menu elements on most website, enhancing the productivity for accessibility and power users.

PowerNav automatically begins functioning on websites with navigation menu elements. When a user press any key in keyboard, the tool looks for clickable elements text that start with the entered characters.
